==Legs==
On 29 April 2014, it was announced that the play off would take place over two legs, with each side hosting one leg.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.afp.com/en/node/2338991|title=Anglo-french play-off dates announced|website=afp.com|accessdate=14 September 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140430050339/http://www.afp.com/en/node/2338991|archive-date=2014-04-30|dead-url=yes|df=}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.facebook.com/PremiershipRugby/posts/10152346338216539?stream_ref=10|title=Premiership Rugby|website=www.facebook.com|accessdate=14 September 2017}}</ref> The draw to decide which team would hold home-advantage for each leg took place on 6 May 2014<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.premiershiprugby.com/news/31547.php#.U2jd_ldnBbw|title=Play-off details announced|website=premiershiprugby.com|accessdate=14 September 2017}}</ref>

