==Result==
[[Wasps RFC|Wasps]] won the playoff 50 - 35 on aggregate and qualify for the [[2014–15 European Rugby Champions Cup]].  [[Stade Français]] will play in the [[2014–15 European Rugby Challenge Cup]].

